query:
UPDATE 
                http_trigger 
            SET 
                workspaced_route = $1,
                wrap_body = $2,
                raw_string = $3,
                authentication_resource_path = $4,
                script_path = $5, 
                path = $6, 
                is_flow = $7, 
                http_method = $8, 
                static_asset_config = $9, 
                edited_by = $10, 
                email = $11, 
                is_async = $12, 
                authentication_method = $13, 
                summary = $14,
                description = $15,
                edited_at = now(), 
                is_static_website = $16,
                error_handler_path = $17,
                error_handler_args = $18,
                retry = $19
            WHERE 
                workspace_id = $20 AND 
                path = $21
